Team 348 ARMS! ARMS! ARMS! is more than happy to present our submission for STORM SURGE CADathon:

M1574 - 2022 - FR - A001 (1)1920×1080 690 KB

We signed up for the competition as ARMS! ARMS! ARMS! and were so glad that the challenge fitted our name and enabled us to use one arm for it all.

We can’t believe we won 1st place!

  • JVN calculation used to get the optimal motor and gear ratio
  • Simple mechanism that can be easily built
  • Low budget

and most importantly an ARM!

A big thank you to Team 1678 for the opportunity to CAD a robot for an incredible game and competition.

Full Storm Surge Field (1)1920×1080 3.79 MB

Submission Sheet

CAD\Renders

More than welcome to contact me with questions on this thread or email (yairr@miscar1574.org)

Expect more cool stuff soon!
